{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "2.200", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "2.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.280", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.800", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.680", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "...\u00a0nach der vertraglichen Regelung"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.440", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0zum Euro\u00a0\u2013"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.120", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gibt es keine Haftung der Gemeinschaft f\u00fcr Verbindlichkeiten der Mitgliedstaaten und keine zus\u00e4tzlichen Finanztransfers."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.200", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sind die Worte Helmut Kohls aus der Bundestagsdebatte vom 23.\u00a0April 1998."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.120", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die CDU-Wahlwerbung zur Europawahl\u00a01999 proklamierte auf die Frage, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.080", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob Deutschland f\u00fcr die Schulden anderer L\u00e4nder aufkommen m\u00fcsste\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.160", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich zitiere \u2013:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.320", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein ganz klares Nein! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.760", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Maastrichter Vertrag verbietet ausdr\u00fccklich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.000", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Europ\u00e4ische Union oder die anderen EU-Partner f\u00fcr die Schulden eines Mitgliedstaates haften."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.160", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So hat man es den W\u00e4hlern versprochen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.040", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kein Euro-Land darf f\u00fcr die Schulden eines anderen Mitgliedstaates haftbar gemacht werden: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.680", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So steht es in den Vertr\u00e4gen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.600", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dies war ein zwingender und elementarer Grundsatz bei der Gr\u00fcndung der Europ\u00e4ischen W\u00e4hrungsunion. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.320", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Offensichtlich ist es Ihnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.160", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die hier schon l\u00e4nger sitzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.640", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "herzlich egal, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.280", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was Sie den B\u00fcrgern versprechen;"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.560", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn sonst h\u00e4tten Sie nicht den fatalen Griechenland-Rettungspaketen und den diversen Rettungsschirmen zugestimmt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "119.600", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der deutsche Steuerzahler muss enorme Haftungsrisiken tragen und daneben mit seinem hart erarbeiteten Geld marode Banken und Staaten retten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "119.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.840", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil diese schlecht gewirtschaftet haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.280", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als Dank schwindet sein Erspartes durch die Negativzinspolitik dahin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.240", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und auch die Zukunft seiner Rente ist dadurch massiv gef\u00e4hrdet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.040", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Politik ist unverantwortlich."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.080", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was hier geschieht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.400", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist nicht nur unmoralisch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.040", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es ist rechtswidrig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.480", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Artikel\u00a0123 des Vertrages \u00fcber die Arbeitsweise der Europ\u00e4ischen Union verbietet die Finanzierung eines Staates durch die Zentralbank ausdr\u00fccklich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.240", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch das Bundesverfassungsgericht hat dies j\u00fcngst in einer Entscheidung bekr\u00e4ftigt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.400", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundesregierung scheinen Urteil und Vertr\u00e4ge jedoch gar nicht interessiert zu haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.040", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man bastelt lieber bereits in Hinterzimmern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.920", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um Debatten und Abstimmungen im Plenum zu umgehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.160", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich frage Sie ganz ehrlich: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.480", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Haben Sie alle eigentlich \u00fcberhaupt gar kein Unrechtsbewusstsein mehr?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.640", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diesem nicht hinnehmbaren Zustand wird sich die AfD, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.400", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Alternative f\u00fcr Deutschland\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.080", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und daf\u00fcr sind wir angetreten\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.920", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit aller Kraft entgegenstellen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.400", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir werden nicht widerspruchslos zusehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.760", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie man uns weiter vor vollendete Tatsachen stellt und die B\u00fcrger kalt enteignet."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.920", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Reden von Angela Merkel, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.320", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wolfgang Sch\u00e4uble, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.640", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Juncker und Emmanuel Macron lassen keinen Zweifel mehr daran, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.440", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die geplante Marschroute des Euro-Raumes folgende ist: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.880", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dauerhafte Vergemeinschaftung der Schulden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "231.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.000", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ein Euro-Finanzminister mit einem eigenen Budget"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.640", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0haupts\u00e4chlich finanziert vom deutschen Steuerzahler, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "239.600", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "versteht sich\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "239.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "242.680", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und ein eigenes Euro-Zonen-Parlament."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "242.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.760", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Von Gewaltenteilung ist \u00fcberhaupt gar keine Spur mehr."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "247.840", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "247.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.160", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist ein Skandal, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.600", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
