   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.960", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Euro sollte dazu f\u00fchren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.440", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Europa zusammenw\u00e4chst. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "258.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.080", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Von einem wahren Friedensprojekt sprach einst Helmut Kohl."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "264.360", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die traurige Wahrheit aber ist\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "264.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "265.520", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das wissen Sie alle\u00a0\u2013: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "265.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "269.080", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Euro hat Europa auseinandergerissen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "269.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "274.080", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die AfD-Fraktion bringt heute ihren ersten Sachantrag in den Deutschen Bundestag ein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "274.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "276.320", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sehr geehrte Damen und Herren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "276.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "277.240", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "277.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "279.160", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das Verfassungs- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "279.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "280.720", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und EU-Vertragsrecht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "280.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "283.160", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Ihnen offensichtlich fremd ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "283.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "284.760", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wieder eingehalten wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "284.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "290.000", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So sieht es n\u00e4mlich aus."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "290.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "291.840", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen damit den B\u00fcrgern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "291.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "292.960", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den Steuerzahlern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "292.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "296.680", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den Sparern und den zuk\u00fcnftigen Generationen eine Stimme geben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "296.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "301.800", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die ihnen in den Jahren der unverantwortlichen Euro-Dauerrettung genommen wurde. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "301.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "303.040", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir fordern deshalb, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "303.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "309.560", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gegen s\u00e4mtliche EZB-Beschl\u00fcsse zum munteren Gelddrucken und zur Verm\u00f6gensvernichtung endlich Klage einzureichen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "309.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "313.560", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Anleihenkaufprogramme sind verfassungswidrig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "313.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "316.880", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und sie versto\u00dfen gegen europ\u00e4isches Vertragsrecht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "316.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "319.720", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sehr geehrte Damen und Herren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "319.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "327.040", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dazu muss der ewigen Euro-Rettung mittels der \u00adTARGET2-Salden endlich ein Ende gesetzt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "327.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "331.400", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit dem Abnicken s\u00e4mtlicher Pseudohilfsprogramme haben Sie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "331.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "333.200", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "werte Damen und Herren der Fraktionen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "333.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "334.840", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die schon l\u00e4nger hier sitzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "334.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "341.160", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unserem Staat und den deutschen Steuerzahlern bereits einen immens hohen Schaden zugef\u00fcgt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "341.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "342.920", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit muss endlich Schluss sein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "342.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "345.000", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die B\u00fcrger haben es satt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "345.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "349.360", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eine abgehobene Politik der arroganten Gutsherrenart auszuhalten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "349.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "354.240", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und es muss endlich wieder zur Rechtsstaatlichkeit zur\u00fcckgekehrt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
